snippet.title: Battle Isle: The Andosia War gameplay (PC Game, 2000)
snippet.description:
Introduction and gameplay for Battle Isle: The Andosia War, PC game produced by Blue Byte in 2000 - http://www.squakenet.com/download/battle-isle-andosia-war/14612/
Battle Isle: The Andosia War is a combination  of strategy and war games, city and base development, and strategic combat, all under the pressures of real-time competition.
Played through modern Windows machine.
Recorded with original sound.

Similar videos you may like:
Metal Fatigue - https://youtu.be/abo9NsUsxCE
Battle Isle - https://youtu.be/73N6s0V_3lU
Battle Isle 93 - The Moon of Chromos - https://youtu.be/o-bknU4XY8s
